| Capability | Status | Source |
|------------|--------|--------|
| Product retrieval (dynamic) | âœ… Working (fetches from `/api/products`) | `shop.html` script, `workers/sbs-products-api.js` |
| Category pills & size filtering | âœ… Working (client-side filtering) | `shop.html` JS |
| Image modal viewer | âœ… Working | `openImageViewer()` |
| Add to basket (local storage) | âœ… Working | `addToCart()` localStorage `sbs-basket` |
| Persist basket across reload | âœ… Working | localStorage load on DOMContentLoaded |
| Remove from basket | âœ… Working | `removeFromCart()` |
| Checkout / order creation | âŒ Not implemented (no UI â†’ orders API only partial) | Missing frontend |
| Pricing integrity | âš ï¸ Placeholder (randomized per load) | `generatePrice()` in worker |
| Inventory sync with D1 | âŒ Not implemented (images-only, no DB join) | Pending Phase 2 Inventory |

Action Items to move from WIP â†’ MVP:
1. Replace random price generator with deterministic price_cents from D1 `inventory`.
2. Introduce `/api/products` endpoint inside main API (joins inventory) or have worker query D1 (Durable binding) instead of only Cloudflare Images API.
3. Implement client-side basket â†’ server order draft creation (`POST /api/orders` with CSRF) and server returns order_number + payment intent placeholder.
4. Add stock validation & status checks (reject `status != active`).
5. Add price integrity guard: server calculates authoritative totals; client displays returned summary.
6. Add UI state for empty inventory, network error retry, and skeleton cards for perceived performance.

Until those are complete: shop is FUNCTIONAL (browse + basket) but not COMMERCIALLY COMPLETE.

### ğŸ§¹ Documentation Debt
Duplicate sections (Design System, Version History, API docs) appear twice â€” schedule a doc normalization pass after Phase 2 Inventory completion.

